{"tid":1431130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登真係有必要開個英文台做文宣","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T01:16:26.000Z","uid":36092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6403dbd4b3230670e5c4a16d6cd95d8bd3ebaff","tid":1431130,"uid":36092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615cec58503476d260589e9ad800becb7b105896","tid":1431130,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=share&amp;v=x5JbM5V9_Lw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dshare%26v%3Dx5JbM5V9_Lw&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=3c25ed1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=share&amp;v=x5JbM5V9_Lw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9644d12bc05e534f2802429a67f3559ac33313","tid":1431130,"uid":298077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:21:30.000Z","msg":"AGREED"},{"pid":"944fac101a489077ae848e4b322a8a796876e6fa","tid":1431130,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"你以為只有得一個user需要英文台嗎？唔信我換過其他user再send同一篇文求連登出英文台<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。<br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.幫推<br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，將入面既post再推<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.堅持每日全部post再一推<br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止"}]}